Look at https://github.com/lefoyer/larrymod

Installing larry mod plugin
---------------------------------------

You need roundcube > 1.1.1 installed.

1. Download the latest version it to the roundcube plugins dir :

    mkdir <path_to_roundcube>/plugins/larrymod

    cd <path_to_roundcube>/plugins/larrymod

    git clone https://github.com/lefoyer/larrymod.git .

2. Add "larrymod" to the plugins list in <path_to_roundcube>/config/main.inc.php, for example :

    $rcmail_config['plugins'] = array('larrymod',);

It works :)


Configuration
-------------

You can customize some settings :

    copy config.inc.php.dist to config.inc.php
    edit config.inc.php as you fancy
